{"id":293943,"type":3,"name":"ラブネスト 下","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/ba/74/293943_DRQ50.jpg","summary":"想うだけなら許して欲しい……。\r\n\r\n旭への恋心を自覚した匡人は、捨て身の告白で旭と一夜を共にする。\r\n告白の返事は保留のまま、表面上は変わらない関係を続けていたが、\r\n以前とは違う旭の甘い態度に匡人の心は期待で揺れた。\r\nしかし、旭の弟・恒生が現れたことで状況は一変。\r\nなぜなら彼は、かつて荒れていた匡人がいたずらに罠にはめ、\r\n恋人と別れるように仕向けた相手で……。\r\n\r\n「チェンジワールド」スピンオフ、完結篇！","info":"<li><span>艺术家: </span><a href=\"/person/14604\">斉藤壮馬</a> / <a href=\"/person/5178\">川原慶久</a> / <a href=\"/person/5602\">山中真尋</a> / <a href=\"/person/5007\">興津和幸</a> / <a href=\"/person/12483\">古川慎</a></li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/18583\">南月ゆう</a></li><li><span>发售日期: </span>2020-02-28</li><li><span>价格: </span>￥3,300</li><li><span>碟片数量: </span>1</li><li><span>厂牌: </span>新書館</li>","collection":{"on_hold":2},"tags":[{"name":"2020","count":1},{"name":"漫画改","count":1},{"name":"斉藤壮馬","count":1},{"name":"BLドラマCD","count":1},{"name":"川原慶久","count":1},{"name":"BLCD","count":1}],"staff":[{"id":14604,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/8c/e3/14604_prsn_kRPr7.jpg","name":"齐藤壮马","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":5178,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/b2/23/5178_prsn_KZack.jpg","name":"川原庆久","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":5602,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/79/4b/5602_prsn_N5v0c.jpg","name":"山中真寻","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":12483,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/15/71/12483_prsn_pXYzu.jpg","name":"古川慎","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":5007,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/9e/df/5007_prsn_LClCs.jpg","name":"兴津和幸","desc":"艺术家"},{"id":18583,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/g/09/ab/18583_prsn_aMc26.jpg","name":"南月ゆう","desc":"原作"}],"relations":[{"id":292947,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/db/d0/292947_7eVVn.jpg","title":"ラブネスト","type":"书籍","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/292947"},{"id":292949,"image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/72/26/292949_0et1C.jpg","title":"ラブネスト 上","type":"其他","url":"https://bgm.tv/subject/292949"}]}